5983-1|date=2017-06-15 }}\n* {{cite book |ref={{harvid|Palla|2000}}\n|last=Palla |first=Marco |series=Interlink Illustrated Histories |title=Mussolini and Fascism |year=2000 |publisher=Interlink Books |location=New York |isbn=978-1-56656-340-6}}\n* {{cite book |ref={{harvid|Pankhurst|1968}}\n|last=Pankhurst |first=R. |title=A Brief Note on the Economic History of Ethiopia from 1800 to 1935 |year=1968 |location=Addis Ababa |publisher=Haile Selassie I University |oclc=434191}}\n* {{cite book |ref={{harvid|USSD|1943}} |title=Peace and War: United States Foreign Policy 1931\u20131941 |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |year=1983 |orig-year=1943 |publisher=State Department |location=Washington, DC |edition=online |url=http://0-www.ibiblio.org.librus.hccs.edu/hyperwar/Dip/PaW/index.html |accessdate=3 September 2017 |oclc=506009610 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170904013854/http://0-www.ibiblio.org.librus.hccs.edu/hyperwar/Dip/PaW/index.html |archive-date=4 September 2017 |url-status=dead |df=dmy-all }}\n* {{cite book |ref={{harvid|Rhodes|1973}}\n|title=The Vatican in the Age of the Dictators: 1922\u20131945 |last=Rhodes |first=A. |authorlink=Anthony Rhodes |year=1973 |publisher=Hodder & Stoughton |location=London |edition= |isbn=978-0-340-02394-5}}\n* {{cite book |ref={{harvid|Safire|1997}} |last=Safire |first=William |title=Lend Me Your Ears: Great Speeches in History |year=1997 |publisher=norton |location=New York |edition=rev. expanded |isbn=978-0-393-04005-0 |url=https://archive.org/details/lendmeyourearsgr00safi }}\n* {{cite book |ref={{harvid|Sbacchi|1997}}\n|title=Legacy of Bitterness: Ethiopia and Fascist Italy, 1935\u20131941 |last=Sbacchi |first=A. |authorlink= |year=1997 |publisher=Red Sea Press |location=Lawrenceville, NJ |edition= |isbn=978-0-932415-74-5}}\n* {{cite book |ref={{harvid|Shinn|Ofcansky|2013}}\n|last1=Shinn |first1=D. H. |last2=Ofcansky |first2=T. P. |series=Historical dictionaries of Africa |title=Historical Dictionary of E