i |year=1937 |oclc=799891187}}\n* {{cite book |first=Ian W. |last=Walker |title=Iron Hulls, Iron Hearts: Mussolini's elite Armoured Divisions in North Africa |publisher=Crowood |year=2003 |location=Marlborough |isbn=978-1-86126-646-0}}\n* {{cite book |last=Willoughby |first=C. A. |year=1990 |orig-year=1939 |series=FMRP 12,13 |title=Maneuver in War |chapter=XI: The Italo-Ethiopian War |pages=230\u2013285 |publisher=Department of the Navy: Headquarters United States Marine Corps |location=Washington, DC |edition=repr. online |chapter-url=http://www.marines.mil/Portals/59/Publications/FMFRP%2012-13%20%20Maneuver%20in%20War.pdf |docket=PCN 140 12130000 |access-date=19 September 2017 |oclc=34869726}}\n\n===Theses===\n* {{cite thesis |last=May |first=M. A. |title=Fuelling Fascism: British and Italian Economic Relations in the 1930s, League Sanctions and the Abyssinian Crisis |type=PhD |url=http://ethos.bl.uk/OrderDetails.do?uin=uk.bl.ethos.482810 |year=2000 |publisher=London School of Economics and Political Science (University of London) |accessdate=19 September 2017 |docket=uk.bl.ethos.482810   |oclc=940362449}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.mtholyoke.edu/acad/intrel/selassie.htm Speech to the League of Nations, June 1936] (full text)\n* [https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=oyX2kXeFUlo British newsreel footage of Haile Selassie's address to the League of Nations]\n* [http://www.regioesercito.it/campagne/etiopia/indexcampetiopia.htm Regio Esercito: La Campagna d'Etiopia]\n* [http://www.icrc.org/Web/eng/siteeng0.nsf/iwpList96/DEB07F09BE30F4B8C1256DB000479398 Ethiopia 1935\u201336: mustard gas and attacks on the Red Cross] ([http://www.icrc.org/web/fre/sitefre0.nsf/html/5RQERS Full version in French]) \u2013 Bernard Bridel, ''[[Le Temps]]''\n* [https://www.sipri.org/sites/default/files/Italo-Ethiopian-war.pdf The use of chemical weapons in the 1935\u201336 Italo-Ethiopian War] \u2013 SIPRI Arms Control and Non-proliferation Programme, October 2009\n* [http://www.workmall.