gory:Italy in the Second Italo-Ethiopian War| ]]\n[[Category:Persecution of ethnic groups by fascist regimes]]\n[[Category:Wars involving Ethiopia|Italo-Ethiopian War, Second]]\n[[Category:Wars involving Italy|Italo-Ethiopian War, Second]]\n", "name_user": "DavideVeloria88", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Second_Italo-Ethiopian_War"}
{"title_page": "Ministry of Family, Labour and Social Policy (Poland)", "text_new": ":''Not to be confused with a similarly named [[Ministry of Labour and Social Policy (1987-2003)]].''\n{{Infobox Government agency\n|agency_name     = Ministry of Family, Labour and Social Policy\n|nativename      = <small>Ministerstwo Rodziny, Pracy i Polityki Spo\u0142ecznej</small>\n|logo            =Polish_Governmental_and_Diplomatic_Plaque.svg\n|logo_width      =\n|logo_caption    =\n|seal            =\n|seal_width      =\n|seal_caption    =\n|image           = Ministerstwo Rodziny, Pracy i Polityki Spo\u0142ecznej ul. Nowogrodzka.jpg\n|image_caption   = Ministry headquarters at Nowogrodzka Street\n|formed          =16 November 2015\n|preceding1      = \n|preceding2      =\n|jurisdiction    =\n|headquarters    = ul. Nowogrodzka 1/3/5, [[Warsaw]]\n|employees       = \n|budget          =\n|chief1_name     = [[Marlena Mal\u0105g]] \n|chief1_position = Minister of Family, Labour and Social Policy\n|chief2_name     = \n|chief2_position =\n|parent_agency   = [[Council of Ministers of the Republic of Poland|Council of Ministers]]\n|website         = [http://www.mpips.gov.pl/ www.mpips.gov.pl]\n|footnotes       =\n|chief3_name=|chief3_position=|chief4_name=|chief4_position=|chief5_name=|chief5_position=|chief6_name=|chief6_position=|chief7_name=|chief7_position=|chief8_name=|chief8_position=|chief9_name=|chief9_position=|parent_department=}}\n'''Ministry of Family, Labour and Social Policy of the Republic of Poland''' was formed in 2005 to administer issues related to [[labour policy|labour]] and [[social policy]] of [[Poland]]. It was named Ministry of Labour and Social Policy until late 2015 when it was renamed to Ministry of Family, Labour and Social Policy.\n\nThe ministry was formed from the former and short-lived [[Ministry of Social Affairs (Poland)|Ministry of Social Affairs]] (created from 2004) and still existing, but reduced [[Ministry of Economy (Poland)|Ministry of Economy]]. From the Ministry of Economy, the new ministry acquired the competences in the fields of employment and combating unemployment, relations and conditions of labor, labor-related benefits, and trade union relations. The social policy part of the ministry gives it competences over the issues of family issues, and social benefits and welfare.\n\nThe ministry supervises the [[Zak\u0142ad Ubezpiecze\u0144 Spo\u0142ecznych]].\n\nSince 2019 the current Minister of Labour and Social Policy is [[Marlena Mal\u0105g]]\n\n==List of ministers==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+\n!\n!Portrait\n!Name \n!Party \n! colspan=\"2\" |Term of Office\n![[Prime minister|Prime Minister]] (cabinet)\n|-\n! style=\"background:{{Law and Justice/meta/color}};\"|\n|[[File:El\u017cbieta Rafalska (2017).JPG|90px]]\n|[[El\u017cbieta Rafalska]]\n|[[Law and Justice]]\n|16 November 2015\n|4 June 2019\n|[[Beata Szyd\u0142o]] ([[Cabinet of Beata Szyd\u0142o|Szyd\u0142o]]), \n[[Mateusz Morawiecki]] [[Cabinet of Mateusz Morawiecki|(Morawiecki]])\n|-\n! style=\"background:{{Law and Justice/meta/color}};\"|\n|[[File:Bo\u017cena Borys-Szopa Sejm 2015.JPG|60px]]\n|[[Bo\u017cena Borys Szopa]]\n|[[Law and Justice]]\n|4 June 2019\n|15 November 2019\n|[[Mateusz Morawiecki]] [[Cabinet of Mateusz Morawiecki|(Morawiecki]])\n|-\n! style=\"background:{{Law and Justice/meta/color}};\"|\n|[[File:Spotkanie z pani\u0105 Marlen\u0105 Mal\u0105g.jpg|90px]]\n|[[Marlena Mal\u0105g]]\n|[[Law and Justice]]\n|15 November 2019\n|Present\n|[[Mateusz Morawiecki]] [[ Second Cabinet of Mateusz Morawiecki|(Morawiecki II]])\n|}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.mpips.gov.pl/ Ministry of Labour and Social Policy of the Republic of Poland]\n\n{{Ministries of the Republic of Poland}}\n\n[[Category:Government ministries of Poland|Labour and Social Policy]]\n[[Category:Labour relations in Poland|Poland]]\n[[Category:Social affairs ministries|Poland]]\n[[Category:Labour ministries|Poland]]\n[[Category:Ministries established in 2005|Poland, Labour and Social Policy]]\n[[Category:2005 establishments in Poland]]\n[[Category:Welfare in Poland]]\n\n{{Poland-gov-stub}}\n{{environment-stub}}\n", "text_old": ":''Not to be confused with a similarly named [[Ministry of Labour and Social Policy (1987-2003)]].''\n{{Infobox Government agency\n|agency_name     = Ministry of Family, Labour and Social Policy\n|nativename      = <small>Ministerstwo Rodziny, Pracy i Polityki Spo\u0142ecznej</small>\n|logo            =Polish_Governmental_and_Diplomatic_Plaque.svg\n|logo_width      =\n|logo_caption    =\n|seal            =\n|seal_width      =\n|seal_caption    =\n|image           = Ministerstwo Rodziny, Pracy i Polityki Spo\u0142ecznej ul. Nowogrodzka.jpg\n|image_caption   = Ministry headquarters at Nowogrodzka Street\n|formed          =16 November 2015\n|preceding1      = \n|preceding2      =\n|jurisdiction    =\n|headquarters    = ul. Nowogrodzka 1/3/5, [[Warsaw]]\n|employees       = \n|budget          =\n|chief1_name     = [[Marlena Mal\u0105g]] \n|chief1_position = Minister of Family, Labour and Social Policy\n|chief2_name     = \n|chief2_position =\n|parent_agency   = [[Council of Ministers of the Republic of Poland|Council of Ministers]]\n|website         = [http://www.mpips.gov.pl/ www.mpips.gov.pl]\n|footnotes       =\n|chief3_name=|chief3_position=|chief4_name=|chief4_position=|chief5_name=|chief5_position=|chief6_name=|chief6_position=|chief7_name=|chief7_position=|chief8_name=|chief8_position=|chief9_name=|chief9_position=|parent_department=}}\n'''Ministry of Family, Labour and Social Policy of the Republic of Poland''' was formed in 2005 to administer issues related to [[labour policy|labour]] and [[social policy]] of [[Poland]]. It was named Ministry of Labour and Social Policy until late 2015 when it was renamed to Ministry of Family, Labour and Social Policy.\n\nThe ministry was formed from the former and short-lived [[Ministry of Social Affairs (Poland)|Ministry of Social Affairs]] (created from 2004) and still existing, but reduced [[Ministry of Economy (Poland)|Ministry of Economy]]. From the Ministry of Economy, the new ministry acquired the competences in the fields of employment and combating unemployment, relations and conditions of labor, labor-related benefits, and trade union relations. The social policy part of the ministry gives it competences over the issues of family issues, and social benefits and welfare.\n\nThe ministry supervises the [[Zak\u0142ad Ubezpiecze\u0144 Spo\u0142ecznych]].\n\nSince 2019 the current Minister of Labour and Social Policy is [[Marlena Mal\u0105g]]\n\n==List of ministers==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+\n!\n!Portrait\n!Name \n!Party \n! colspan=\"2\" |Term of Office\n![[Prime minister|Prime Minister]] (cabinet)\n|-\n! style=\"background:{{Law and Justice/meta/color}};\"|\n|[[File:El\u017cbieta Rafalska (2017).JPG|90px]]\n|[[El\u017cbieta Rafalska]]\n|[[Law and Justice]]\n|16 November 2015\n|4 June 2019\n|[[Beata Szyd\u0142o]] ([[Cabinet of Beata Szyd\u0142o|Szyd\u0142o]]) , \n[[Mateusz Morawiecki]] [[Cabinet of Mateusz Morawiecki|(Morawiecki]])\n|-\n! style=\"background:{{Law and Justice/meta/color}};\"|\n|[[File:Bo\u017cena Borys-Szopa Sejm 2015.JPG|60px]]\n|[[Bo\u017cena Borys Szopa]]\n|[[Law and Justice]]\n|4 June 2019\n|15 November 2019\n|[[Mateusz Morawiecki]] [[Cabinet of Mateusz Morawiecki|(Morawiecki]])\n|-\n! style=\"background:{{Law and Justice/meta/color}};\"|\n|[[File:Spotkanie z pani\u0105 Marlen\u0105 Mal\u0105g.jpg|90px]]\n|[[Marlena Mal\u0105g]]\n|[[Law and Justice]]\n|15 November 2019\n|Present\n|[[Mateusz Morawiecki]] [[ Second Cabinet of Mateusz Morawiecki|(Morawiecki II]])\n|}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.mpips.gov.pl/ Ministry of Labour and Social Policy of the Republic of Poland]\n\n{{Ministries of the Republic of Poland}}\n\n[[Category:Government ministries of Poland|Labour and Social Policy]]\n[[Category:Labour relations in Poland|Poland]]\n[[Category:Social affairs ministries|Poland]]\n[[Category:Labour ministries|Poland]]\n[[Category:Ministries established in 2005|Poland, Labour and Social Policy]]\n[[Category:2005 establishments in Poland]]\n[[Category:Welfare in Poland]]\n\n{{Poland-gov-stub}}\n{{environment-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Iridescent", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eList of ministers:Cleanup andtypo fixing,typo(s) fixed: ,  \u2192 ,", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ministry_of_Family,_Labour_and_Social_Policy_(Poland)"}
